Customer Care

development:

mvn spring-boot:run # or run nabor-cc (shared) configuration

+

npm i
npm start
npm run dev
npm run tdd
npm run e2e
npm run lint
npm run webpack
npm run build
npm run serve

generate angular 2 components using angular-cli:

npm i -g angular-cli
cd src/app
ng g c my-component

idea configuration:
- choose use .editconfig settings
- do not compile typescript files with idea

if you have any problems with build on 'install node and npm' phase:
rm -rf applications/cc/src/web/node applications/cc/src/web/node_modules applications/cc/src/web/npm.tar.gz
